metadata.name: The Nightlight
metadata.description:
6000 x 4500px @ 300ppi
One night, I woke up paralyzed.  I was sitting up slightly, and my head was stuck facing the ceiling.  I felt like something nearby was watching me.  It took all my power to move my head down, but I couldn't see anything except a light and some furniture in the other room.  But I knew something was lurking in the shadows...
